channel.title: The greatest clutch for king ever!
channel.description:
I was BD king. Had a alchy friend. He died. But HE KEPT HEALING ME TILL N5.. I executed MM two times.....Then When it went down.. To A FOOL, A MERC, A POSSESOR, and Me., Oh also a physician, BUT WE DON'T TALK ABOUT HIM
he died...
I had 6 guards. I wasn't giving up. I was like ATTACK ME ALL YOU WANT. I HAVE 6 GUARDS. I AM NOT GIVING UP. so.. we went on. Till the fool got bored voted up the possessor.
I basically won this for the BD.. being the last BD alive.
king op
